{% markdown %}
Space tokens create predictable rhythm and meaningful proximity. They use `rem` units so spacing scales proportionately with the root font size.

Use `--wa-space-scale` to increase or decrease all spacing at once. The default multiplier is `1`. For example, `--wa-space-scale: 1.25` makes all spacing 25% larger.
{% endmarkdown %}

